c: 6
v: 128
t: "On the day He gathers them all together (He will say), \"Oh you, the species of jinn! A great many humans have you lured and led astray! Their allies among the human kind (would exclaim), \"Our Lord, we did enjoy (and benefit from) each other´s alliance, and now we have completed the term you had appointed for us.\" Allah will say, \"The hellfire is your home. You will live there forever, unless Allah wills otherwise. Indeed, your Lord is the Wisest and the most Aware"